@node "change" "g"
 
  The default icons are in MWB style, because I like MWB very much.
  But if you are a NewIcons user (nice too) you possibly dislike
  this icons. You can replace the drawer icon and the game icon
  easily. Just open a shell and do something like this.


  Copy ram:mydrawer.info dh0:CoolInstaller/dat/def_drawer.info
       ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^                       ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
        Your new icon                          replace old drawer
  

 Additionally to def_drawer.info (the drawer icon) there`s 
 def_game.info (the game icon). You can replace it by the
 same script. 

 Of course you can use a directory manager like the famous
 DirOpus for those operations (is there really anybody who
 does this like this??)

 If you`ve really problems with this, mail me, let`s see
 what we can do.

@endnode

