@node "wasmacht" ""

  dA cOOL iNSTALLER (DCI) installs nearly every standard Amiga DOS
  game/demo on your harddisk.

  DCI has powerful features. If the game/demo is ECS, DCI degrades 
  the computer to ECS. (not in the unreg. version)
 
  DCI can install games/demos with more disks too.

  A trackdisk.device emulation is finally in work and will be
  present in one of the next versions. Have a look at @{"History" link "history"}.
  
  Installing a game/demo is as easy as possible.
  See how @{"easy" link "ques"} it is.

@endnode

